        <div facs="#eSc_textblock_b620cf2e">
            <figure>
                <desc resp="#np">
                    Illustration of a Welte-Mignon.
                </desc>
            </figure>
            <lb />DESIGN
            OF OAK CASE
        </div>

            <div facs="#eSc_textblock_f1d73028">
                <head>
                    <hi rendition="#c">
                        <lb />THE
                        <lb />Welte-Mignon 
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <lb />Brings to your home the actual living perform-
                <lb />ances of
                <persName corresp="https://d-nb.info/gnd/11918625X">Hofmann</persName>,
                <persName corresp="https://d-nb.info/gnd/124379923">Lhevinne</persName>,
                <persName corresp="https://d-nb.info/gnd/118986724">Paderewski</persName>,
                <lb />
                <persName corresp="https://d-nb.info/gnd/116204400">Bloomfield-Zeisler</persName>
                and a hundred other great
                <lb />pianists.
            </div>
            
            <div facs="#eSc_textblock_b2073d40">
                <p>
                    <seg ana="#technical_invention" resp="#np" type="topic">
                        <lb />The science of musical reproduction has progressed
                        <lb />through the various stages-experiment, medioc-
                        <lb />rity, excellence-but until the introduction of the
                        <lb />Welte-Mignon
                        <lb />it has never reached supreme per-
                        <lb />fection. But today the science has reached its
                        <lb />apex, the goal has been attained and beyond the splendid
                        <lb />achievement realized in the Welte-Mignon it is im-
                        <lb />possible to go.
                    </seg>
                </p>
                <p>
                    <lb />The Welte-Mignon brings to the
                    <lb />music-lover the actual performances of every great living pian-
                    <lb />ist.
                    
                    <seg ana="#immortality">
                        It perpetuates these performances so that fu-
                        <lb />ture generations will enjoy the music of our
                        <lb />present-day virtuosos when their personalities are
                        <lb />but misty memories.
                    </seg>
                </p>
                <p>
                    <seg ana="#analogy_to_phonograph" resp="#np" type="topic">
                        <lb />What the Victor is doing for the famous singers
                        <lb />of the world the Welte-Mignon is
                        <lb />accomplishing for the pianists.
                    </seg>
                    But with this difference: The
                    <lb />Victor registers the voice vibrations on the disc,
                    <lb />whereas the sensitive reproducing devices of the
                    <lb />Welte-Mignon are of such nature that every dupli-
                    <lb />cate performance IS MADE DIRECTLY ON THE
                    <lb />PIANO,
                    <seg ana="#exact_reproduction">
                        thereby reproducing in every detail of
                        <lb />touch, tone and technique the actual
                        <lb />renditions of the pianists, in every sense their original per-
                        <lb />formances.
                    </seg>
                </p>
                <p>
                    <lb />The series of instruments containing the repro-
                    <lb />duction devices are the Welte-Mignon, as illustrated
                    <lb />above, the Steinway-Welte, an upright Steinway
                    <lb />piano combined with the Welte-Mignon, and the
                    <lb />Cabinet-Welte, which may be attached to any grand
                    <lb />or upright piano of any make.
                </p>

                <lb />Call or Write for Descriptive Literature
                <lb />We will gladly mail to interested parties descriptive literature and
                <lb />prices of the Welte-Mignon instruments. We are especially desirous
                <lb />that you come to our store and give these instruments your personal
                <lb />inspection.

                <hi rendition="#c">
                    <lb />FREE RECITALS DAILY FROM 9 A. M. TO 5 P.M-Fourth Floor.
                </hi>

                <hi rendition="#c">
                    <lb /><orgName key="birkel">Geo J. Birkel Company</orgName>
